#: ../../files/access_webdav.rst:223
msgid "Accessing files using macOS"
msgstr "Komma åt filer i macOS"

#: ../../files/access_webdav.rst:225
msgid ""
"The macOS Finder suffers from a `series of implementation problems "
"<http://sabre.io/dav/clients/finder/>`_ and should only be used if the "
"Nextcloud server runs on **Apache** and **mod_php**, or **Nginx 1.3.8+**. "
"Alternative macOS-compatible clients capable of accessing WebDAV shares "
"include open source apps like `Cyberduck <https://cyberduck.io/>`_ (see "
"instructions `here "
"<https://docs.nextcloud.com/server/latest/user_manual/files/access_webdav.html#accessing-"
"files-using-cyberduck>`_) and `Filezilla <https://filezilla-project.org>`_. "
"Commercial clients include `Mountain Duck <https://mountainduck.io/>`_, "
"`Forklift <https://binarynights.com/>`_, `Transmit <https://panic.com/>`_, "
"and `Commander One <https://mac.eltima.com/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Finder i macOS har `flera implementeringsproblem "
"<http://sabre.io/dav/clients/finder/>`_ och bör endast användas om "
"Nextcloud-servern körs med **Apache** och **mod_php** eller **Nginx "
"1.3.8+**. Alternativa macOS-kompatibla klienter som kan komma åt WebDAV-"
"delningar är bland annat appar med öppen källkod som `Cyberduck "
"<https://cyberduck.io/>`_ (se anvisningarna `här "
"<https://docs.nextcloud.com/server/latest/user_manual/files/access_webdav.html#accessing-"
"files-using-cyberduck>`_) och `Filezilla <https://filezilla-project.org>`_. "
"Kommersiella klienter är bland annat `Mountain Duck "
"<https://mountainduck.io/>`_, `Forklift <https://binarynights.com/>`_, "
"`Transmit <https://panic.com/>`_ och `Commander One "
"<https://mac.eltima.com/>`_."

